v_1,\dots,v_n
\sum_{k=1}^n\big(\deg_o(v_k)\big)^2=\sum_{k=1}^n\big(\deg_i(v_k)\big)^2\;,
\sum_{k=1}^n\left(\big(\deg_o(v_k)\big)^2-\big(\deg_i(v_k)\big)^2\right)=0\;.
